quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  3,133,"Ne yilushile obulesheli bwa Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi, nende omukunda kwomwikulu (Jannah) kwobubambalifu bwako ni likulu nende eshialo, kwarecheshelwa abaria Nyasaye."
  3,134,"Balia barusinjia omwandu nibenyala nende nibali mubutinyu, nende beyikalilanga liruma nende baleshelanga Abandu. Ne Nyasaye yachama abakholi bamalayi."
  3,135,"Balia nibakhola ashifuolo nohomba nibekholela obubii, betsulila Nyasaye mana basabe eshileshelo khutsimbi tsiabu. Ne ni wina uleshelanga tsimbi ulali Nyasaye? Ne shibatsilililanga okhukhola akabakhola nabo nibamanyile tawe."
  3,136,"Abo omurungo kwabu ni obulesheli okhurula khu Nyasaye wabu Omulesi, nende emikunda chomwikulu chiburangamwo emialo, balimenyamwo tsinyanga tsioosi, ne ni omulayi muno omurungo kwa abakholi bamalayi."
  3,137,"Imbeli wenyu chiamala okhubura emilukha eminji. Kho chende khushialo mulole indukho ya balia abakatsula."
  3,138,"Khuno nookhwinoosilia abandu, nende obulunjifu nende amachelo khubalia baria Nyasaye."
  3,139,"Ne mulateshele tawe, ne mulabeelela tawe. Toto enywe nenywe ba hekulu nikali mbu toto muba Abasuubili."
  3,140,"Obubii nibubanyoola, manye mbu toto abandu bandi abo boosi banyoolwa nende obubii shinga obo. Ne etso nitsinyanga tsia khukalukhanilinjia abandu, kho Nyasaye amanye Abasuubili, ne abukule mwinywe aberwa khunjila yiyie. Ne Nyasaye shiyachama abamabii tawe."